name: Fidelity Global Equity+ Fund
longDescription: The Fund invests primarily in equity securities of companies located anywhere in the world. The Fund can invest in these securities either directly or indirectly through investments in underlying funds, which may include liquid alternative mutual funds. The Fund invests primarily in equity securities of companies located anywhere in the world.
